videos.description: QB Seth Boomer finds WR Jarion Anderson on the crossing route to give the Golden Hurricane a 7-0 lead.
videos.headline: Tulsa strikes first with 14-yard TD pass

videos.description: QB Blake Barnett takes a shot at the end zone, but DB Keanu Hill picks him off to preserve the Golden Hurricane's 10-3 lead.
videos.headline: Tulsa protects lead with INT

videos.description: RB Jordan Cronkrite gets through a hole and blazes his way to the end zone to knot the score at 10-10.
videos.headline: South Florida opens 2nd half with game-tying 66-yard run

videos.description: RB Shamari Brooks finds an opening and goes untouched to the end zone, making it 17-10 Golden Hurricane.
videos.headline: Tulsa reclaims lead with 10-yard TD run

videos.description: RB Shamari Brooks scores his second touchdown in as many possessions to extend the Golden Hurricane lead to 24-10.
videos.headline: Brooks strikes again to double Tulsa's lead

videos.description: QB Blake Barnett tucks it and runs, getting across the goal line to cut the Golden Hurricane's lead to 24-16.
videos.headline: South Florida stays alive with 1-yard QB run

videos.description: QB Blake Barnett makes a man miss and beats the defense to the end zone, cutting Tulsa's lead to 24-22.
videos.headline: Barnett's 12-yard run brings South Florida with 2

videos.description: QB Blake Barnett is stacked up by the Tulsa defense, as the Golden Hurricane preserve their 2-point lead with under 3 minutes to play.
videos.headline: South Florida fails to tie game on 2-point conversion

videos.description: Blake Barnett is on target to WR Tyre McCants, who takes it all the way to the 5-yard line, setting up Jake Stone's 22-yard game winner.
videos.headline: Barnett sets up game-winning FG with 32-yard strike

videos.description: Down 24-10 in the 4th quarter, Blake Barnett runs in two TDs and fuels South Florida to a winning field goal, avoiding an upset.
